From cou.: 11 The solvents used were acetone, cyclohexane and dichloromethane (residue analysis grade, Panreac, Barcelona, Spain). Anhydrous sodium sulfate for residue analysis was purchased from Panreac. All pesticide reference materials were obtained from Dr. Ehrenstorfer (Augsburg, Germany). The following pesticides were tested: ethoprophos, dimetoate, diazinon, parathion-methyl, chlorpyrifos-methyl, pirimiphos-methyl, parathion-ethyl, and carbophenothion.
From Soup: 11 The solvents used were acetone , cyclohexane and dichloromethane (residue analysis grade, Panreac, Barcelona, Spain). Anhydrous sodium sulfate for residue analysis was purchased from Panreac. All pesticide reference materials were obtained from Dr. Ehrenstorfer (Augsburg, Germany). The following pesticides were tested: ethoprophos , dimetoate, diazinon , parathion-methyl , chlorpyrifos- methyl , pirimiphos- methyl , parathion- ethyl , and carbophenothion .
