From cou.: 20 50 g of each commodity were spiked with a mixture of the pesticides at the following concentrations: ethoprophos and carbophenothion, 0.15 mg L−1; diazinon, 0.30 mg L−1; and all the other pesticides, 0.60 mg L−1. These concentrations were chosen on the basis of their different MRLs.5,6 After evaporation of the solvent using an air stream, the sample was mixed thoroughly and homogenised for 2 min. Then the sample was extracted and re-dissolved with 5 mL of cyclohexane that contained a caffeine concentrate at 1.0 mg L−1. 1µL was then injected into the GC-NPD.
From Soup: 20 50 g of each commodity were spiked with a mixture of the pesticides at the following concentrations: ethoprophos and carbophenothion , 0.15 mg L −1 ; diazinon , 0.30 mg L −1 ; and all the other pesticides , 0.60 mg L −1 . These concentrations were chosen on the basis of their different MRLs. 5,6 After evaporation of the solvent using an air stream, the sample was mixed thoroughly and homogenised for 2 min. Then the sample was extracted and re-dissolved with 5 mL of cyclohexane that contained a caffeine concentrate at 1.0 mg L −1 . 1µL was then injected into the GC-NPD.
